Red Soil	Southern & Eastern India	Millets, Pulses
Laterite Soil	Western Ghats, Northeast	Tea, Coffee, Spices
Desert Soil	Western Rajasthan	Bajra, Mustard
Mountain Soil	Himalayan states	Apple, Tea, Maize
ğŸŒ¦ Major Cropping Seasons in India
