ğŸ“Š Important Notes About Real-Time Data

Real-time agricultural data (production, market price, acreage) is dynamic and depends on:

Rainfall

Market demand

Government policy

Irrigation availability

Official live data sources in India include:

Ministry of Agriculture reports

Agmarknet

eNAM portal

